<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>{{title}}</title>
  </head>
  <body
    style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;"
  >
    <div>
      <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <img
          src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dvvirefzi/image/upload/v1743526776/klarify-logo_v2yhrm.png"
          alt="Logo"
          class="logo"
          style="max-width: 120px;"
        />
      </div>

      <div
        style="padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; border: 1px solid #eee; color: #1e1c1c;"
      >
        <div
          style="padding: 5px; text-align: center; font-weight: 500; font-size: 24px; color: #000000;"
        >
          Goal Reminder: {{goalTitle}}
        </div>
        <p>{{greeting}}</p>
        <p>Here's an update on your goal progress:</p>
        
        <div style="margin: 20px 0; background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px;">
          <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 5px;">
            <span>Progress:</span>
            <span>{{currentProgress}}/{{targetProgress}} ({{progressPercentage currentProgress targetProgress}}%)</span>
          </div>
          <div style="height: 10px; background-color: #e0e0e0; border-radius: 5px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
            <div style="height: 100%; width: {{progressPercentage currentProgress targetProgress}}%; background-color: #0f084e; border-radius: 5px;"></div>
          </div>
          <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between;">
            <span>Time remaining:</span>
            <span>{{daysRemaining}} day{{#if (gt daysRemaining 1)}}s{{/if}}</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p>Keep up the good work! You're making progress toward your goal.</p>
        <p>Need motivation? Remember why you set this goal in the first place!</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br />Klarify Team</p>
      </div>
      <div
        style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; color: #888; font-size: 0.8em;"
      >
        <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</p>
        <p>Â© {{year}} Klarify. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>